latestIgtvVideos.title: Blend It Raw Apothecary Review
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Hi Guys,

I am back with another IGTV Video and this time it's my review about one of the beautiful brands which I have used till now. that is Blend It Raw Apothecary. @blenditrawbeauty

I was introduced to this Brand through instagram and @paintedcharisma , Mahesweta mam uses their hibiscus mask so I was curious to use that. 

then I DM that brand on instagram and Arushi suggested me the products exactly for my concerns and I am using it from past 1 month and today I will share my experience with you all. 

what I like about @blenditrawbeauty 
1. they work with our small farmers of India which in a way helping our economy .

2. their products are Raw, unrefined and pure. 

3. most of their products are for both skin and hair. 

4. They are 100% transparent about their ingredients. 

5. they create every product in fresh batch.

6. they are very much customer friendly. 

What all I have ordered. 

❤️ kalonji oil
❤️ Nettle hydrosol
❤️ bhringaraj powder
❤️ hibiscus powder. 

My thoughts about the products. 

I loved them. my main concern was hair fall and these products helped me in reducing that to another level. I am so happy with the results and as far as hair growth is concerned, I will try it for 3 months and I am sure I will see the results. 

Will I buy from this brand again. 
💯 yes. no doubt about it. ☺️☺️

I hope you all will like this video. in case you find it helpful then do share it with your friends and family it will mean a lot. thank u. ☺️
